#          alongside cobra / gin / grpc-go / fsnotify); used by:
#            * Hugo (since v0.20 — config.toml + front-matter)
#            * confd (etcd/consul config templates)
#            * Caddy (some configs)
#            * Shopify/sarama (Kafka client)
#            * Drone CI (early versions)
#            * gnostic (Google OpenAPI tool)
#            * gokrazy (Go-only Raspberry Pi distro)
#            * obs-scene-switcher (THIS)
#            * 50,000+ Go applications
#          obs-scene-switcher — 38+ stars on muesli/
#          obs-scene-switcher; used by Linux livestreamers.
